                <head>29. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d29fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Council, Institutional Files, Box 95, <gloss target="#t_SCC_1"
                            >SCC</gloss> 082, Space Policy, <gloss target="#t_ASAT_1">ASAT</gloss>
                        Hostile Acts and Tests, 6/1/78. Top Secret; Codeword. The meeting took place
                        in the White House Situation Room.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            from="1978-06-01T15:50:00-04:00" to="1978-06-01T18:00:00-04:00">June 1,
                            1978, 3:50–6:00 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <list type="subject">
                    <head>SUBJECT</head>
                    <item>
                        <gloss target="#t_ASAT_1">ASAT</gloss> Treaty</item>
                </list>
